import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Tabs } from 'antd';
const { TabPane } = Tabs;

const Tab = () => (
  <Tabs defaultActiveKey="1" centered>
    <TabPane tab="Tab 1" key="1">
      <Link to='/withEmails'>
        With Emails
      </Link>
    </TabPane>
    <TabPane tab="Tab 2" key="2">
      <Link to='/withoutEmails'>
        Without Emails
      </Link>
    </TabPane>
  </Tabs>
);

export default Tab
